   <text:p text:style-name="lg">6. n pdure crescui, n pdure nscui,<text:line-break/>Acas dac m-aduse<text:line-break/>Hor-mprejuru-mi se puse.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">MASA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">7. M dusei n munte s-mi caut caii. Caii nu-i gsii, dar vzui vntul rsturnnd pmntul.</text:p>
