   <text:p text:style-name="lg">23. Ln peste ln,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">La mijloc e vn,<text:line-break/>Vna se zgrcete,<text:line-break/>Lna se cltete.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">MNUA</text:p>
