   <text:p text:style-name="P35">FEREASTRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">26. Ce e nalt ca casa,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">Verde ca mtasa,<text:line-break/>i amar ca fierea,<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10">i dulce ca mierea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">NUCUL</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">27. Pan mpnat,<text:line-break/>Pe ap lsat,<text:line-break/>Cu mn de om,<text:line-break/>Cu voie de domn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">MOARA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">28. Am zece frai: cinci subt streain i cinci afar ; pe cei de sub streain i plou i pe cei de afar, nu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">CND TOARCE LA IN I UD DEGETELE CU CARE TRAGE FIRUL DIN CAIER</text:p>
