   <text:p text:style-name="P17">60 .* Azi aci, mine n Focani. Cv. XIII, Cgl. 41 0.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17">1. Azi are, satur zece si mine flmnd petrece. P.p. v., 50 .</text:p>
